archimate:Contract.name: [TOS] Mini Broker Terms of Service (Contract)
archimate:Contract.documentation:
These are the conditions under which alerts will be delievered to a user.
Conditions include a limit on the number of alerts per visit, processing time over the filter per visit, other terms related to the user's ability to accept data as they are orginating. TBD: Is alerts per visit an average or a single visit limit?
